OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEnergy firms must help     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcustomers with unpaid bills
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Energy suppliers will now have to help 
OL,6, struggling customers with their energy 
OL,7, bills after new rules came into effect.
OL,9,FFrom 14 December Ofgem requires        
OL,10,Fcompanies to contact vulnerable        
OL,11,Fcustomers if they miss two monthly or  
OL,12,Fone quarterly payment and check to see 
OL,13,Fif they are having financial problems  
OL,14,Fwith their bills.                      
OL,16,FEnergy firms must help by offering     
OL,17,Faffordable payment plans or repayment  
OL,18,Fholidays if appropriate.               
